/**
 * Common code between `ɵɵclassProp` and `ɵɵstyleProp`.
 *
 * @param prop property name.
 * @param value binding value.
 * @param suffix suffix for the property (e.g. `em` or `px`)
 * @param isClassBased `true` if `class` change (`false` if `style`)
